Registering to the platform is free and you only pay for the services you need. They also offer accessible psychological attention 24 hrs a day 365 days a year.

The platform will be available in iOs, Android and desktop versions. A clinical profile will be available for you to fill-in that will make your consultations faster and will also facilitate how you share your information with other health professionals. Your medical profile is stored in a safe manner by using protected data bases, only you will be able to share its information with the health professional of your choosing.
